Data collected:
- App usage data (e.g. feature engagement, screen time)
- Crash logs (via Firebase Crashlytics)
- Device type and OS version

Data usage:
- Analytics and app performance monitoring
- Bug fixing and crash diagnostics

Data shared:
- None

Data encryption:
- Yes, all data transmitted and stored securely

User control:
- No sign-in required
- No user account system currently
- Users can uninstall the app to remove local data
